## What it does

Robofang is an **agentic orchestration layer** that connects a fleet of MCP servers, a local inference stack, and physical/virtual hardware into a single, human-sovereign system.

The core loop:

```
Perceive → Reason (Council) → Act (MCP hands) → Audit → Update memory
```

It is not a wrapper around an API. It is a locally-running system where:

- A **Council of agents** (Foreman / Labor / Satisficer) breaks complex tasks into specifiable, auditable steps — no black-box single-shot calls
- A **live fleet map** tracks every MCP server you have: tool schema, port, health signal — queryable by agents and visible in the dashboard
- **Four tiers of "Hands"** give agents increasing dexterity over your digital, virtual, and physical world
- **Local inference first**: Council operations run on Ollama (RTX 4090 — Llama 3.3 70B, Qwen 2.5 32B); cloud APIs are the fallback, not the default
- A **Resonite/OSC bridge** lets agents embody virtual avatars at 30 Hz joint control — the same code path that drives physical robots via ROS 2

## Quick start

```powershell
git clone https://github.com/sandraschi/robofang
cd robofang
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -e .
copy .env.example .env   # fill in your credentials
cd dashboard; npm install; npm run build; cd ..
.\start_all.ps1
# Dashboard at http://localhost:10864
```

---

## The four tiers of Hands

> *"Agents Need Hands"* — [steipete](https://steipete.com/)

Hands are not a monolith. Dexterity requires a capability spectrum:

| Tier | Name | What it means |
|------|------|---------------|
| 1 | **SimpleHands** | Execute code, touch files, call terminals — atomic, one-shot |
| 2 | **FlowHands** | Multi-step workflows with state, self-correction via telemetry |
| 3 | **AppHands** | MCP-powered reach into your ecosystem: email, Discord, Home Assistant, Plex, Calibre, Hue, Tapo, Ring... |
| 4 | **RoboHands** | Physical / virtual embodiment via ROS 2, OSC, Blender, Unity, Resonite |

Each tier builds on the last. A council agent with all four active can: read your calendar, decide what matters, generate a 3D asset in Blender, and publish it to a live Resonite session — without leaving the loop.

In our opinion, **Agents Need Bots.** Robofang is the orchestration layer where cognitive architecture meets physical and virtual capability, transforming AI from a predictive spectator into a sovereign actor.

