## Features

Robofang inherits the robust communication features of **OpenClaw** and layers on a large set of media and generation capabilities.

Deep integration for **media consumption** (Plex, Calibre, Immich) so your agent knows what you've read and watched. **Media generation** via Blender or Inkscape for professional assets. A **virtualization pipeline** bridging VRChat-style social spaces to industrial tools like Unity3D.

